[color=green]In a nutshell :[/color]

Cryptos Platform (CryOS) is a next generation cryptocurrency project with a focus on mobile development and global use of resources

We will soon publish our own API which is already an essential part of our apk - architecture and will make the implemention of our technology simple for third party publishers

As our app was built using "Unity Engine", we have the idea in mind to publish a mobile game in the future

Supply will be spread to the community by rewards and future application functionality ( when coinsale has ended )

Core Wallets (Windows & Linux) + Daemon exist but are not yet published to ensure a clean launch and successfull coinsale

For more information, please visit our website  ;)


